---
import ContentPage from "../../../components/ContentPage.astro";
import ContentPanel from "../../../components/ContentPanel.astro";
---

<ContentPage
  title="About our house | Tiny Temptation Tubs"
  lang="en"
  path="/en/about/"
  heading="About our house"
  centerBody={false}
>
  <ContentPanel>
    <div class="hand-text flex flex-col gap-6">
      <h2>What is <em><strong>Tiny Temptation Tubs</strong></em>?</h2>
      <p>
        Tiny Temptation Tubs is an RP &amp; ERP bathhouse, a place for
        relaxation, connection, and closeness.
      </p>
      <p>
        We offer our guests a warm and stylish environment where roleplay,
        conversations, shared evenings, and special moments take center stage.
        Whether you seek quiet relaxation, deep conversations, or more sensual
        RP, you are free to express yourself here - as long as everything
        remains respectful and consensual.
      </p>
      <h2>Who is this place for?</h2>
      <p>Our house is open to everyone who:</p>
      <ul class="hand-text-list">
        <li>enjoys RP and community</li>
        <li>is looking for a safe and respectful space</li>
        <li>wants to experience relaxed or more intimate interactions</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        All races are welcome, including Lalafell. We take great care to keep
        this place safe and comfortable for everyone.
      </p>
      <p>
        Tiny Temptation Tubs is more than just a place — it is a space for
        connection, stories, and shared experiences.
      </p>
    </div>
  </ContentPanel>
</ContentPage>
